OPC UA C++ Server & Client SDK V6.00

EnumNumericNodeId Reference

Top  Previous  Next

The OPC standard specifies a number of nodeIds which are for standardized nodes (used all in the reserved namespace 0).

These nodeIds are collected in this enumeration, the single members are not listed in the documentation (refer to the UA specification).

EnumNumericNodeId_Null = 0

no valid NodeId.
